{"tid":2115200,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個屋企人衞生意識差既事例","createTime":"2020-07-19T10:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T13:25:35.000Z","uid":297518,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4abb728194e91384327b37fbfaf4ecd3c0b03827","tid":2115200,"uid":297518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:39:14.000Z","msg":"屋企有個阿哥，結左婚搬左出去住<br />\n間唔中會冚家上來我屋企食下飯咁<br />\n<br />\n但佢地好撚仆街，成日戴完啲口罩周撚圍擺<br />\n有時提佢地要做好衞生防疫措施，但佢地話「個肺炎中就中，唔中就唔中架啦，可能我地而家都有菌架，邊個知姐」<br />\n<br />\n喂大佬呀，屋企有老有幼<br />\n你唔諗下自己都諗下d高危人士啦<br />\n<br />\n自撚私到死，完全厚顏無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69abab66617a0e2d64f4bd4114d7ae8477c12bfb","tid":2115200,"uid":332538,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:42:28.000Z","msg":"以前有個類似嘅Post<br />\n跟住有位會員話佢父母為左慳錢<br />\n用廁所水拖地"},{"pid":"2095ab303098843c55b8f025548820e878be66be","tid":2115200,"uid":28960,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:44:56.000Z","msg":"「個肺炎中就中，唔中就唔中架啦，可能我地而家都有菌架，邊個知姐」<br />\n講依句野d人真係好撚on9<br />\n風險都有大細之分啦<br />\n中就中唔中就唔中 咁唔見佢地唔戴口罩出街<br />\non撚9<br />\n又要驚 比人話果陣又講d on9野<br />\n正臭閪"},{"pid":"16dd31b56f698705ab79615afe95bae69548f045","tid":2115200,"uid":297518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69abab66617a0e2d64f4bd4114d7ae8477c12bfb","tid":2115200,"uid":332538,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:42:28.000Z","msg":"以前有個類似嘅Post<br />\n跟住有位會員話佢父母為左慳錢<br />\n用廁所水拖地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:45:14.000Z","msg":"唔撚係呀<br />\n咸水黎wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f152fba534781421de729918cfb4f048aa2f567b","tid":2115200,"uid":297518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2095ab303098843c55b8f025548820e878be66be","tid":2115200,"uid":28960,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score"